}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can&apos;t seem to find the error. In the code above, when I call the log, I get the values from &lt;code&gt;mContactsFromFirebase&lt;/code&gt;, but the &lt;code&gt;getContactsFromFirebase()&lt;/code&gt; method return an empty list. Could you help me please?&lt;/p&gt;
